[{"id":"FT548940","type":"longtextV2","stimulusHtml":"<p>The work shown is an example of a mihrab.</p>\n\n<p>Analyze how specific characteristics of this mihrab reflect the beliefs of Islam. How would this mihrab have facilitated religious practices?&nbsp;</p>\n","features":[{"type":"sharedpassage","html":"<img alt=\"The image is a picture of a tiled wall with a shallow recess in the wall. The tilings in the wall are tessellated. The majority of the tiles are two shades of blue, with white and gold accents. There is some Arabic script around the border of the wall and in the recessed area.\" height=\"660\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/media.academicmerit.com/50bce6359dc356c7f70945c991b51994/original.png\" width=\"450\">"}]}]